"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0803-1463363-paris-2024-ecstatic-biles-takes-seventh-olympic-gold\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"An \\\"ecstatic\\\" Simone Biles won her seventh Olympic gold medal and third of this Games in the women's vault.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An \\\"ecstatic\\\" Simone Biles\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"her seventh Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 31, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"third\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 71}, {\"ngram\": \"this Games\", \"from\": 75, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's vault\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American was all smiles after landing a Yurchenko double pike, known as the Biles II, on her first vault, taking only a small step back and scoring a massive 15.700.\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 113, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8062872519608961, \"rank\": 0.24024928401222154, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128801457, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"smiles\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 136}, {\"ngram\": \"the Biles II\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 197}, {\"ngram\": \"her first vault\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"only a small step\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her second vault was scored at 14.900, giving her an overall mark of 15.300 and leaving her well clear of Brazil's Rebecca Andrade in silver, while another American, Jade Carey, took bronze.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9552715515938874, \"rank\": 0.04653546734039039, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999859028, \"rank\": 1.3988267440707813e-11, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8062872519608961, \"rank\": 0.24024928401222154, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her second vault\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"an overall mark\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super excited, ecstatic for how my vaults were,\\\" said Biles.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my vaults\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to perform them well, and I think you saw that today.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I put in a lot of work to be able to perform that vault (the Yurchenko double pike) well.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"that vault\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited I got to show that here during finals today.\\\"\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was welcomed into Bercy Arena with huge cheers and shrugged off a tumble on the Yurchenko in practice, performing it almost flawlessly when it really counted.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"huge cheers\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"a tumble\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"the Yurchenko\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old has also won gold here in the team and all-around competitions and could yet surpass her tally of four golds from Rio.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999961232683857, \"rank\": 3.876746744573304e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"all-around competitions\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"her tally\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"four golds\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a triumphant return to the Olympic stage for Biles, who was one of the biggest stories of the Tokyo Games when, as favourite to win multiple golds, she pulled out of most events after suffering from 'the twisties', where a gymnast loses sense of where they are in the air.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a triumphant return\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stories\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple golds\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"most events\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"a gymnast\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She faced high-profile criticism in some quarters and has been working with a therapist in Paris.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1434, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999952252, \"rank\": 4.779506541081654e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high-profile criticism\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"some quarters\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"a therapist\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The negative comments are painful up to a certain point,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The negative comments\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain point\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They hurt but I am still in therapy working on all that, to make sure my mental health is well.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they (the critics) are really quiet now, so that's strange.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the critics\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After all these years of putting the mental work in, it's paid off.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all these years\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental work\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am super excited to be on this stage again.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics is such a draining process for the athletes, and it's multiple days of competition, so you definitely have to be on top of your mental as well as physical (health).\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"such a draining process\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple days\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"physical (health\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as we are doing that, then we are good.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so far I feel good.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once we are out here, the floor is our stage.\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"our stage\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It feels so freeing for us because we are in our element, we are having fun, we are doing what we love to do.\\\"\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"our element\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles will conclude her campaign on Monday when she goes in the beam and floor finals.\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"her campaign\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"the beam and floor finals\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch the 2024 Olympic Games with 14 hours of televised action on RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player each day.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"score\": 0.9994238889060038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c92\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"14 hours\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"televised action\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Player\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to extensive radio coverage on RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 and 2fm's Game On and follow each moment from Paris on RT\\u00c9.ie, the RT\\u00c9 News app and all RT\\u00c9 digital platforms.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2480, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999952252, \"rank\": 4.779506541081654e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\", \"score\": 0.9356964890387794, \"rank\": 0.061574627460354234, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extensive radio coverage\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Radio\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"all RT\\u00c9 digital platforms\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to the daily RT\\u00c9 Sport Olympics Podcast.\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the daily RT\\u00c9 Sport Olympics Podcast\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:PA \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Source\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"PA \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"fr